d of the tournament. With their extraordinary performance in 1982 FIFA World Cup, they again reached the semifinal of the tournament and finished third place. Poland got eliminated from the round of 16 in 1986 FIFA World Cup. Poland did not advance to the FIFA World Cup for three consecutive times in the year 1990, 1994 and 1998. In 2002 FIFA World Cup Poland got eliminated from the group stage and same happened in the next FIFA World Cup 2006. Poland did not qualify for the 2010 FIFA World Cup and 2014 FIFA World Cup. But Poland would play the tournament I 2018 FIFA World Cup.</p>
