http://wikiceleb.com/egypt-road-russia-fifa-world-cup-2018/";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-01-23 22:17:25";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-01-23 16:32:25";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=634";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"644";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-12-25 23:16:42";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-25 17:31:42";s:12:"post_content";s:14653:"<p style="text-align: justify;">The FIFA World Cup is the most prestigious and respectable tournament in the world football and with<a href="http://wikiceleb.com/russia-host-fifa-world-cup-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> Russiaâ€™s</a> 2018 tournament edition almost at our doorstep, many strikers, wingers or many players will be seeking to show their capabilities and to write their names in the world football. Talking about the strikers and wingers, they are in the eye of football fans because they are more responsible for scoring goals. Forwards in the football team are the players who play closest to the opposing teamâ€™s goal and are therefore score more goal than other teammates. And a winger is an attacking player who is responsible to beat opposing full-backs, crosses from a wide position with their speed, skill, and vision. Here are 11 of the best strikers/wingers in the world.</p>
